sp.p:
(raising himself, and looking ferociously at Leonard and
Jessie.) Curses on you both! this will send me across the seas, I know ;
but I shall return, and then beware—I live but for vengeance.

All right, master, butter, eggs, and ducks, and chickens, and calves, and
pigs, and Becky, be all packed in comfortable —there only wants you and me to
make up the family party;
